name: Stuck in a Castle Alpha 0.01
description:
So this is my first prototype game I made by myself using some free assets from around the internet. I am unlikely to be returning to this project to make a fleshed out game. So i hope you enjoy this.

The controls are fixed to keyboard.

Note: If you are having low FPS issues or others try running the game on an alternate browser or on browser default settings.

Thank you

Saksham "Gabber1110" Agarwal
